7ec5333b2221025","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"陪我一齊響街邊食燒賣果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅<br />\n邊個俾負皮同我企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d427ee703e4680a67542c2cb6612a46ff51f0481","tid":642263,"uid":56729,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"望住佢係廚房傻更更煮緊野食個憨鳩樣就好想係後面攬住佢叫佢做老婆<br />\n唔知點解覺得煮野食既時候特別有老婆味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372da9d9ae3d3e195666a929fd2aa23701257abd","tid":642263,"uid":76488,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85200e2b89e8b5e07b45fb2991e7772ff554b4a6","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36c0872c37db15d546c6f47642b3094c72e997f2","tid":642263,"uid":61171,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d9442a2d69a8c14fbbe36a197ec5333b2221025","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"陪我一齊響街邊食燒賣果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅<br />\n邊個俾負皮同我企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"我地好似響到格劍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed84def23127c340f7b3f2befe4aa4a6c07b508e","tid":642263,"uid":71524,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"係我事業同學業都失意個時扶返起我個兩段時間<br />\n問心佢同佢一家真係一個好好人<br />\n係我學業失意個陣佢冇介意過我係個公園到喊成兩個鐘咁聽我講<br />\n係我事業失意個陣，除咗佢陪我，佢呀爸呀媽都俾咗好多鼓勵我<br />\n有一次我負到一個地步咁問佢：你本身住緊私樓，點解唔介意同我呢個窮撚，仲要同我一齊涯？你d同事冇笑你咩？<br />\n佢就答我：咁係人都會有起有跌架啦，係我跌倒既時候你都扶起我，點解我唔可以扶返起你。笑我同你？我笑返佢地俾層樓揸住個春袋做人。年年可以同你同埋兩家人一齊去旅行我已經心滿意足。差唔多日日有人返完通宵仲要開車過黎送我返工，呢個司機我唔會放佢走架啦<br />\n<br />\n就係呢刻我同佢講：多謝你陪住我咁耐，唔係有你，我諗我一定撐唔住，司機呢個位我唔介意做足一世<br />\n<br />\n宜家佢屋企人成日密密地夾埋我屋企人叫我地快d結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b392a063b59792c766e5f62d016e222e4fbfbf49","tid":642263,"uid":134226,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"85200e2b89e8b5e07b45fb2991e7772ff554b4a6","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36c0872c37db15d546c6f47642b3094c72e997f2","tid":642263,"uid":61171,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d9442a2d69a8c14fbbe36a197ec5333b2221025","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"陪我一齊響街邊食燒賣果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅<br />\n邊個俾負皮同我企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"我地好似響到格劍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:42:47.000Z","msg":"條女攞住支竹籤督鳩你～～<br />\n「係你自己話唔要㗎喎小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n你啤完佢一陣 擰返轉頭食燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻衰妹又督鳩你 仲要笑笑口咁～～～<br />\n你再啤住佢<br />\n「你係咪想我今晚督到你聽朝坐輪椅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n隻衰妹唔出聲 但係仲係笑笑口咁<br />\n你都廢鳩事理佢 繼續食燒賣等條衰妹等陣冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『咁你要餵飽我㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 』<br />\n「咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n你差啲啃親 遞咗兜燒賣俾條女 <br />\n隻衰妹已經陰陰嘴笑<br />\n你膠都廢事俾 喺個袋度攞支水嚟飲<br />\n擰返轉頭<br />\n隻衰妹已經食梗兜燒賣 咬下咬下塊下唇咁望住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『飽晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 』<br />\n你已經忍唔住笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『咁你今晚諗住點餵我吖...』"},{"pid":"216abb553ff1545dd8bcf9d010f0e207c5b9a04f","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"b392a063b59792c766e5f62d016e222e4fbfbf49","tid":642263,"uid":134226,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"85200e2b89e8b5e07b45fb2991e7772ff554b4a6","tid":642263,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36c0872c37db15d546c6f47642b3094c72e997f2","tid":642263,"uid":61171,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅<br />\n邊個俾負皮同我企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"我地好似響到格劍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:42:47.000Z","msg":"條女攞住支竹籤督鳩你～～<br />\n「係你自己話唔要㗎喎小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n你啤完佢一陣 擰返轉頭食燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻衰妹又督鳩你 仲要笑笑口咁～～～<br />\n你再啤住佢<br />\n「你係咪想我今晚督到你聽朝坐輪椅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n隻衰妹唔出聲 但係仲係笑笑口咁<br />\n你都廢鳩事理佢 繼續食燒賣等條衰妹等陣冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『咁你要餵飽我㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 』<br />\n「咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n你差啲啃親 遞咗兜燒賣俾條女 <br />\n隻衰妹已經陰陰嘴笑<br />\n你膠都廢事俾 喺個袋度攞支水嚟飲<br />\n擰返轉頭<br />\n隻衰妹已經食梗兜燒賣 咬下咬下塊下唇咁望住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『飽晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 』<br />\n你已經忍唔住笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n『咁你今晚諗住點餵我吖...』"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"你係咪痴線架大佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n